 placed alongside, then spoon around some of the salsa."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_chillistuffedchicken_84289","title":"Chilli-stuffed chicken with tomato salsa and crushed potatoes","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"10 to 30 mins","cookingMins":30,"totalMins":60},"serves":"Serves 1","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
