 ice cream onto a sheet of cling film into a rectangle as long as the Swiss roll tin and approximately 12.5cm/5in wide. Place the frozen strawberry mousse on top. Wrap in cling film encasing the strawberry mousse into the chocolate ice cream. Roll into cling film and leave in the freezer to firm up again. Unroll the sponge and layer with a thin spreading of the jam.","Place the firm ice cream roll on top and roll together. Cut off any uneven ends, re-wrap in greaseproof paper and return to the freezer to freeze. ","Squeeze to make everything adhere. Unwrap and place on a serving platter. Arrange the dipped strawberries on top. Scatter over some dehydrated strawberries and serve."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_chocolate_and_strawberry_83139","title":"Chocolate and strawberry lime ice cream roll","time":{"preparation":"over 2 hours","preparationMins":120,"cooking":"over 2 hours","cookingMins":120,"totalMins":240},"serves":"Makes 1 large ice cream roll","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":true,"recommendations":0}
