ices and dust with icing sugar."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_chocolateyulelog_93127","title":"Chocolate yule log","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"10 to 30 mins","cookingMins":30,"totalMins":60},"serves":"Serves 6-8","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":true,"recommendations":0}
