e batter in batches, like pancakes. ","To serve, divide the chicken between four plates and serve a waffle with each. Garnish with some lamb’s lettuce and orange segments. "],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_citrus_jerk_chicken_with_93427","title":"Citrus jerk chicken with cornmeal waffles","time":{"preparation":"overnight","preparationMins":null,"cooking":"1 to 2 hours","cookingMins":120,"totalMins":120},"serves":"Serves 4","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
