ta and preserved lemon","time":{"preparation":"overnight","preparationMins":null,"cooking":"10 to 30 mins","cookingMins":30,"totalMins":30},"serves":"Serves 2 as a main, or 4 as a starter","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
