de. Drizzle the chilli jam over the fish and garnish with the coriander cress and a spoon of crème fraîche."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_fillet_of_mackerel_with_51845","title":"Fillet of mackerel with warm pak choi, beans and chilli jam","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"10 to 30 mins","cookingMins":30,"totalMins":60},"serves":"Serves 4","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
