oked through.","For the broadbeans, leeks and asparagus, cook the leeks and asparagus in the remaining 30ml/1fl oz of vegetable stock with the butter, onions, sugar, salt and pepper until almost cooked. Add the broad beans and cook in the glaze for a few minutes more.","To serve, spoon the cauliflower purée onto the centre of the plates. Dress the trout on top. Place the vegetables on top. Mix the sauce with a hand blender to aerate it and spoon the resulting foam over the fish. Garnish with the fresh herbs and season to taste with salt, pepper and lemon juice."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_fillet_of_sea_trout_with_74118","title":"Fillet of sea trout with baby leeks, broad beans and asparagus","time":{"preparation":"less than 30 mins","preparationMins":30,"cooking":"30 mins to 1 hour","cookingMins":60,"totalMins":90},"serves":"Serves 4","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
