ons and mix together.","To serve, place a pile of salad in the centre of each of four plates. Pile up the grilled anchovies next to the salad and serve immediately."],"url":"www_bbc_co_uk_food_recipes_grilledbutterfliedan_87801","title":"Grilled 'butterflied' anchovies with Caesar salad","time":{"preparation":"30 mins to 1 hour","preparationMins":60,"cooking":"10 to 30 mins","cookingMins":30,"totalMins":90},"serves":"Serves 4","image":"https://food.files.bbci.co.uk/kandl-food/1911/images/bbc_placeholder.png","isVegetarian":false,"recommendations":0}
